  "texts": [
    "The results are reported in Table 2, from which we observe:• In general, ToolRec outperforms all baselines on the ML-1M and Amazon-Book datasets.",
    "The performance improvement can be attributed to the efficacy of our designed ToolRec framework.",
    "By delving into various facets of the item pool and utilizing LLMs to guide the exploration process, it can more effectively align with the user's intent.",
    "• ToolRec and ToolRec 𝐵 consistently demonstrate improved performance compared to their respective underlying models (i.e., SAS-Rec and BERT4Rec).",
    "This confirms the superiority of the ToolRec framework and underscores its adaptability."
  ]
}